message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which has been meticulously crafted to provide exceptional value and quality. This product is worth more than $120 to me, but I believe in making it accessible to those who appreciate its unique benefits. For you, I am offering this product at an exclusive price of $150. It's a great opportunity to experience something truly special. If you're interested, let me know and we can proceed with the transaction.
